description:
Originally released in 2003 as the second entry in the Fatal Frame series,
the full remake of the Japanese-style horror classic Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly is set to launch on March 12, 2026 

In this haunting horror adventure, twin sisters who lose their way in an abandoned village haunted by restless wraiths must use the Camera Obscura—a camera that captures and seals away the unimaginable—to battle the spirits and uncover the truth hidden in the darkness.

author: Xbox
description:
War Thunder’s new major update 'Spearhead' has arrived with a variety of interesting vehicles for all kinds of playstyles. The Hawk 200 provides nimble firepower for Great Britain, while the Dutch Fokker D.XXIII (23) brings some classic Second World War fun. France gets the modern and potent EBRC Jaguar as an end of the line light tank, while Great Britain welcomes the Chieftain 900, featuring a more powerful engine. The AH-56 Cheyenne with a unique chopper design comes as a squadron vehicle for the USA, while several nations receive some mighty ships with large guns. And last but not least, Stalingrad and Carpathians have received a beautiful makeover, all while retaining their familiar layout!

description:
Discover three groundbreaking machines in the Formula Legends: Tech Pack DLC. Inspired by the boldest eras of racing innovation, each car brings unique technology, daring design, and thrilling performance to the track.

TramTram Cyclone – A fearless seventies design built around experimental aerodynamic technology. Master its unique handling and experience the raw power of its innovation.

Fyrex Mid 70 – An audacious multi-wheel marvel that redefines traction and control. Take on corners with impossible grip and feel every ounce of its mechanical ingenuity.

Jorsey BeeSting – Sleek, balanced, and lightning-quick. This nineties classic embodies engineering elegance and championship spirit.

author: Xbox
description:
Start from zero in a tale of restoration and retribution!

The free demo of OCTOPATH TRAVELER 0 is available to download and play today on Xbox Series X|S and Windows PC! It lets you play through the opening of the game, the first chapter of the three different story arcs of the Retribution story and the first chapter of the Restoration story - or for three hours. You can continue your adventure on 4th December as your save data will carry over to the full game.

Embark on a brand new adventure of your own creation.
